D

do_part1() - Static method in class Driver
Reads a list of input file names from "Part1_input_file_names.txt" and processes each file according to the given specifications, writing valid records to output files and writing syntax errors to "syntax_error_file.txt".
do_part2() - Static method in class Driver
This method reads book records from input files specified in "Part2_input_file_names.txt", validates the price, year and ISBN of each record, creates Book objects and stores them in a two-dimensional array based on their genre.
do_part3(Book[][]) - Static method in class Driver
Allows the user to view and navigate through a list of book files, selected from a sub-menu.
